        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　釋五種人謂須陀洹八萬劫得菩提乃至辟支佛十千劫得菩提義現病品第十八案。",
        "translation": "He explained the case of the five kinds of people who attain enlightenment in 80,000 eons as a stream entrant ... and up to 10,000 eons as a pratyekabuddha, which is the eighteenth category of manifest illness.",
