        "translation": "It's therefore without illness.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0476b06_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊世人有病或坐或臥(至)云何默然右脇而臥。",
        "translation": "Bhagavān, when people are sick, they sometimes sit or lay down (to) why do they quietly lay on their right side?",
