        "source_sentence": "次答云何而得近最勝無上道也。",
        "translation": "\"How did he then approach the most excellent unsurpassed path?",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a05_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "上云自然得成。",
        "translation": "The above statement says that it's naturally attained.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a06_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今轉近為得。",
        "translation": "Now, it's a change from recently attained to attained.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a06_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但說五人者。",
        "translation": "He simply said there are five people.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a06_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以斷結定故。",
        "translation": "It's because they've cut the bonds of concentration.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a07_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "凡夫定位。",
        "translation": "Ordinary people are conditioned.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a07_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無劫數之限也。",
        "translation": "There's no limit to the number of eons.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a07_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八萬劫者。",
        "translation": "It's 80,000 eons.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a07_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "後云得菩提心。",
        "translation": "Later, it's called attaining the mind of enlightenment.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a08_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦云八萬劫住處。",
        "translation": "It's also called the abode of 80,000 eons.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a08_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是小涅槃。",
        "translation": "This is lesser nirvāṇa.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a08_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "似是菩提心成就耳。",
        "translation": "It seems to be the accomplishment of the mind of enlightenment.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a09_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "思惟煩惱。",
        "translation": "'The afflictions of contemplation.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a09_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "小乘斷之。",
        "translation": "The lesser vehicle stops them.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a09_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不必在菩薩。",
        "translation": "It doesn't have to be among bodhisattvas.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a10_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "劫數如此。",
        "translation": "This is the case for a number of eons.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a10_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故知偏愛易斷。",
        "translation": "Therefore, it's clear that it's easy to stop partial craving ...",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a10_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "等悲難成也。",
        "translation": "It's difficult to achieve equal compassion.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a11_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "法瑤曰。",
        "translation": "Fayao said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a11_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "因表如來無病得命病者。",
        "translation": "\"The Tathāgata who manifests the absence of illness and obtains life as an illness is the meaning of mind.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a11_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心之義也。",
        "translation": "It's also the meaning of mind.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a12_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二乘有病。",
        "translation": "The two vehicles are sick.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a12_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不能發心。",
        "translation": "They can't arouse their minds.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a12_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "要從佛聞法也。",
        "translation": "They must hear the Dharma from the Buddha.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a12_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫利根雖不從佛聞法。",
        "translation": "Although the sharp faculties don't hear the Dharma from the Buddha, they themselves will arouse the mind.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a13_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而自發心。",
        "translation": "Instead, they themselves will arouse the mind.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a13_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "知此二人。",
        "translation": "He knows these two people.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a13_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以得近無上道也。",
        "translation": "That's why they've approached the unsurpassed path.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a14_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曇讖曰。",
        "translation": "Dharmakṣema said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a14_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五種人者。",
        "translation": "\"There are five kinds of people.",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a14_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從須陀洹。",
        "translation": "From stream entrant ...",
        "source": "T37n1763_026:0477a15_13",
